{"tid":942303,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"返shift都要OT係咪閪工","createTime":"2018-12-15T14:54:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-16T16:02:24.000Z","uid":114887,"like":52,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"965d226bfa9ab22212bb2d187643018506c1738f","tid":942303,"uid":114887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T14:54:53.000Z","msg":"我份閪工就返shift既 差唔多日日都要ot半個鐘<br />\n但又成撚日要我做埋隔離department既野<br />\n下星期既更表可以去到星期六甚至星期日先出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n琴日我本身返10點至7點既更<br />\n無啦啦同我講7點有event呀你返埋先走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後我OT左兩個半鐘 咁既閪工係咪quit得<br />\n但我又未過probation<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁既閪工quit啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n廢青捱下都唔得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c905a7b74da24b4d9ad87adb98dbbfaa28bce5b","tid":942303,"uid":114887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T14:55:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0169da72b97451a0e36737dd9e55699f7f2efdd5","tid":942303,"uid":114887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T14:57:55.000Z","msg":"求屌醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49aee6c67431d67936c3d46d73d69951839285db","tid":942303,"uid":114887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T15:02:20.000Z","msg":"大家發表下意見啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d556704a8bb9cab363c2ef32ed5d720c1ccd362","tid":942303,"uid":54025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T15:03:11.000Z","msg":"月薪幾多"},{"pid":"57dc305da6ad9bb7e3e0c8d3824c1f753c391d33","tid":942303,"uid":27568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T15:03:51.000Z","msg":"走啦<br />\n使咩理probation"},{"pid":"a21b079fd994c642872e